# NihongoRoute AI Development Rules

## 🎨 Styling & Design System
- **BANNED**: Never use static Tailwind color utilities (e.g., `bg-white`, `text-gray-900`, `bg-red-500`, `dark:bg-slate-800`).
- **MANDATORY**: Use 100% **Semantic CSS Variables**:
  - `bg-background`, `text-foreground`
  - `bg-primary`, `text-primary-foreground`
  - `bg-secondary`, `text-secondary-foreground`
  - `bg-success`, `bg-warning`, `bg-destructive`
  - `bg-muted`, `bg-card`, `border-border`
- **Aesthetic**: Use `.glass` utility for cards/overlays.

## 📂 Directory Structure
- **lib/**: Pure TypeScript only. **NO JSX/TSX**.
- **components/ui/**: Global primitive components.
- **components/features/**: Domain-specific logic and UI.
- **app/**: Routing and page composition.

## 📡 Data Fetching
- **BANNED**: No time-based revalidation (`export const revalidate = ...`).
- **MANDATORY**: Use `sanityFetch` from `@/lib/sanity.fetch` with appropriate cache tags (e.g., `tags: ['lesson']`).

## ♿ Accessibility & Typography
- **Furigana**: Use `0.55em` relative scale for `<rt>`. Prefer `SmartJapanese` component.
- **Buttons**: Icon-only buttons MUST have an `aria-label`. Decorative icons MUST have `aria-hidden="true"`.
